full_title: What Was I Made For? by Billie Eilish
title: What Was I Made For?

description.plain:
With “What Was I Made For?” FINNEAS once again returns with melancholic production that contrasts with the Barbie movie’s upbeat soundtrack. This also marks the seventh single for the movie’s soundtrack, which Billie Eilish announced the track’s release on her Instagram – proclaiming that she was one of the mystery artists.

This piece takes an in-depth inspiration from Billie’s struggles of continuing her purpose in life as she opened up about her struggles to find her passion for writing and creating music. The song’s meaning can also interpret Barbie’s own spiritual journey to discover herself in the real world as she experiences it throughout the movie.
